# Interview Questions

### Q1. Which property checks whether a CheckBox is selected?

`Checked`

---

### Q2. Which property groups RadioButtons?

`GroupName`

---

### Q3. Which property retrieves the selected item from a DropDownList?

`SelectedItem`

or

`SelectedValue`

---

### Q4. Which event occurs when a DropDownList selection changes?

`SelectedIndexChanged`

---

### Q5. Which control supports multiple selections?

ListBox (when `SelectionMode="Multiple"`)

---

### Q6. Which property stores data in a HiddenField?

`Value`

---

### Q7. Which event occurs when a Calendar date changes?

`SelectionChanged`

---

### Q8. Which control should you use to store an Employee ID without displaying it?

HiddenField

